---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="お問い合わせありがとうございます｜錦乃"
  description="お問い合わせを受け付けました。"
>

<section class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden bg-[#140f0d]">

  <img
    src="/images/contact-form-bg.png"
    alt=""
    class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
    draggable="false"
  />

  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/45"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center px-8">

    <div class="thanks-show max-w-3xl rounded-[2.8rem] border border-white/20 bg-white/10 p-14 text-center text-white backdrop-blur-xl">

      <p class="tracking-[0.45em] text-sm">
        THANK YOU
      </p>

      <h1
        class="mt-6 text-5xl leading-tight"
        style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;"
      >
        お問い合わせありがとうございます。
      </h1>

      <p
        class="mt-10 leading-9 text-white/90"
        style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif;"
      >
        内容を確認のうえ、順次ご返信いたします。<br>
        数日経っても返信が届かない場合は、<br>
        迷惑メールフォルダもあわせてご確認ください。
      </p>

      <div class="mt-14 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-5">

        <a
          href="/"
          class="rounded-full border border-white px-10 py-4 transition duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:text-black"
        >
          TOPへ戻る
        </a>

        <a
          href="/contact/"
          class="rounded-full border border-white/40 px-10 py-4 transition duration-300 hover:border-white hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          CONTACTへ戻る
        </a>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<style>

.thanks-show{

opacity:0;

animation:
thanksFade 1s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1) forwards;

}

@keyframes thanksFade{

0%{

opacity:0;

transform:
translateY(60px)
scale(.96);

}

70%{

opacity:1;

transform:
translateY(-8px)
scale(1.02);

}

100%{

opacity:1;

transform:
translateY(0)
scale(1);

}

}

</style>

</Layout>